# Alt+Tab Foreground Sync and Feature Hotkey Latch (Mandatory — Do Not Regress)

**Status:** Verified working on Windows (2026-07-24, v0.8.293–v0.8.294). User-confirmed: Alt+Tab away and back to linked main target must **not** leave feature hotkeys dead until PIPBONG is focused once.

## Symptom

Main target focused → hotkeys work → Alt+Tab away → Alt+Tab back → hotkeys dead → focus PIPBONG once → hotkeys work again.

**Not** the same as user-held Shift release ([physical-keyboard-preservation.mdc](./physical-keyboard-preservation.mdc)).

## Root cause (two layers)

| Layer | Detail |
| ----- | ------ |
| Foreground sync (v0.8.293) | WinEvent must queue `onForegroundWindowChanged` on UI thread; empty-caption games need process-path profile/capture match; `FeatureHotkeyGate` must **not** block `syncProfileToForegroundWindow` |
| Hook latch (v0.8.294) | Missed KEYUP / mouse UP during Alt+Tab → toggle `armed=false` or mouse `buttonDown=true` → hook swallows next hotkey without firing |

## Required architecture

| API | Role |
| --- | ---- |
| `foregroundWindowEventProc` | `QMetaObject::invokeMethod` → `onForegroundWindowChanged` (not `PostMessageW` alone) |
| `onForegroundWindowChanged` | Alt-release → `flushDeferredProfileSwitchIfIdle` + `resetHookLatchState`; profile sync; capture adopt; `maybeResetHotkeyLatchForForeground`; `finishForegroundSessionGate` |
| `HotkeyManager::resetHookLatchState` | `hold keyDown=false`, `toggle armed=true`, `mouse buttonDown=false`; **no** `hotkeyHoldEnded` emit |
| `maybeResetHotkeyLatchForForeground` | Once per linked-target foreground HWND (`m_lastHotkeyLatchResetForegroundHwnd`) |
| `ensureForegroundReadyForFeatureHotkey` | From `onHotkeyTriggered` / `onHotkeyHoldStarted`: profile + capture resync + latch reset |

## Anti-patterns

- Capture/profile sync only (v0.8.289–0.8.292) — insufficient for latch stuck state
- `resetHookLatchState` every 50 ms poll — breaks hold mode
- Emit hold-ended from latch reset
- Require PIPBONG focus to heal hotkeys after Alt+Tab

## Manual verify

Alt+Tab away/back **without** focusing PIPBONG; keyboard toggle + mouse side-button bindings; repeat 5×.

